&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Manager, SOX Compliance&lt;/strong&gt; to lead execution of ZoomInfo&#39;s SOX program across business process controls, ITACs, and Key Reports. You will manage a global team, partner with external auditors and Finance leadership, and help shape how ZoomInfo manages risk as the company scales. This is a builder role. We want someone who can rationalize a control environment, drive automation, and grow into broader risk advisory responsibilities over time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
